    <item>
      <title>马斯克向共和党提供巨额资金，华尔街助力哈里斯获得现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/wall-street-powers-harris-cash-haul-as-musk-gives-big-to-gop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦选举委员会的最新文件显示，华尔街、硅谷和好莱坞的捐助者为副总统卡马拉·哈里斯 8 月份的筹款激增提供了助力，帮助民主党在总统选举最昂贵的阶段建立了对共和党人唐纳德·特朗普 1.09 亿美元的现金优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/wall-street-powers-harris-cash-haul-as-musk-gives-big-to-gop</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 16:08:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登助手淡化新日铁延期安全审查的重要性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/biden-aide-downplays-nippon-steel-extension-in-security-review</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文 (Jake Sullivan) 淡化了任何暗示，即美国延长新日本制铁公司 (Nippon Steel Corp.) 141 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司 (United States Steel Corp.) 交易的安全审查期限，表明总统乔·拜登 (Joe Biden) 正在对这笔具有政治争议的收购案产生兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/biden-aide-downplays-nippon-steel-extension-in-security-review</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 15:57:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯竞选团队在经济演讲前抨击特朗普对美联储的评论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/harris-campaign-hits-trump-on-fed-comments-before-economy-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的竞选团队严厉批评唐纳德·特朗普对美联储四年来首次降息的批评，并将焦点集中在 11 月总统大选之前的经济问题上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/harris-campaign-hits-trump-on-fed-comments-before-economy-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 15:38:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登主持最后一次四方峰会，敲定对华措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/biden-finalizes-china-measures-as-he-hosts-his-final-quad-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登总统在其任期的最后几个月中继续加大对中国的压力，这一举措表明他在任内为了对抗世界第二大经济体而采取了艰难的应对策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/biden-finalizes-china-measures-as-he-hosts-his-final-quad-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列对真主党采取的新危险态势并未引发战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/inside-israel-s-risky-new-posture-against-hezbollah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列对黎巴嫩真主党采取了更危险、更激进的姿态 — — 爆炸传呼机、袭击贝鲁特并瞄准指挥官 — — 这一转变既是突然的，也是渐进的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/inside-israel-s-risky-new-posture-against-hezbollah</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 14:02:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>传呼机袭击致中东局势陷入危机，加沙协议希望破灭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/gaza-deal-hopes-sputter-as-pager-attacks-bring-mideast-to-brink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿安东尼·布林肯本周飞往中东，自去年 10 月 7 日以来他第 10 次访问中东，但他并不抱太大希望，认为这将有助于加沙战争取得突破。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-21/gaza-deal-hopes-sputter-as-pager-attacks-bring-mideast-to-brink</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Sep 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
